# Test verification receipts live here.
#
# Each scope writes one JSON file (e.g., mobile.json). Pre-push hook reads
# these and validates that every changed test file in the branch has a
# matching content hash recorded — proof the suite actually ran against
# the version being pushed. Receipts ARE tracked in git so reviewers can
# see which suites the author verified before opening the PR.
#
# Generate with: bash scripts/record-test-receipt.sh <scope>
# Validate with: bash scripts/verify-test-receipts.sh
